insert into helpdoc values(newid(), 'http://dev24.sandbox.projectinsight.net/projectinsight.webapp/api/help/model/department', '

Department

Departments are typically assigned to users\, but also projects can be tagged to a department.

NameDescriptionType
Code Gets or sets the string - [Code] - The custom code for the department. Typically used for storing the id or external code for the given department.

Remarks: Default Property

 string
DisplayOrder Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Order] - The order the department appears in lists of departments.

Remarks: Default Property

 integer
Id Gets or sets the guid Id. guid
IdExternal Gets or sets the ProjectInsight.Models.Base.ApiModelBase.IdExternal object which allows the object to be saved with an associated external identification. Used primarily for integrations. IdExternal
IsActive Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Active] - An in-active department cannot be used\, but remains where previously used.

Remarks: Default Property

 boolean
Leader Gets (read only) the User - [Leader] - The department leader.

Remarks: Read Only

 User
Leader_Id Gets or sets the NullableOfT - [Leader] - The department leader. guid
Name Gets or sets the string - [Name] - The name of the department.

Remarks: Default Property

 string
SerializeType Get or Set if the Type should be serialized boolean
Type Gets or sets the string object type for external reference\, rest calls. string
', getUtcDate())
